00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:11,320
Mother.

301
00:31:14,119 --> 00:31:15,128
Master.

302
00:31:19,999 --> 00:31:24,119
Now I see why Ming Xiu
hates demons so much.

303
00:31:25,759 --> 00:31:29,440
