384
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:41,080
Don't make more mistakes.

385
00:38:45,239 --> 00:38:48,080
Maiming, as long as you want it,

386
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:51,560
I will be like I used to be.

387
00:38:55,719 --> 00:38:59,919
